parameters:
\SE[17]Finally... I made it this far. \!\SE[12]Surely,
beyond this...

\SE[52]Oh no...!! You got hurt so much for my sake...!
\SE[13]Wait a moment... I'll heal you...!

\SE[9]I'm fine with just this much... You're still so
overprotective as always.... \SE[37]You haven't changed at
all, Luna....

\SE[45]Laura... you've changed a bit, haven't you? \.You've
become more mature, \.more beautiful, perhaps....
\!\SE[45]Hehe... I feel like falling in love with you all
over again....
\SE[0] Is it okay for the Touching Reunion to end now?

\SE[16]It's been a long time since we last met.... I'll have
Luna return to me. \SE[12]

\SE[54] Will Mama go back to Laura's place? \SE[63] Will I
be alone again...?

\SE[56]I see... Well then, it's fine. I don't care about
everything anymore. \SE[36]It doesn't matter.
\SE[54]Everyone who doesn't like me, they should just die...

\SE[18] (I've come this far... struggling desperately...
but... \SE[54] Can the current me defeat her?)

\SE[45]It's okay. There's nothing to be unsure about.
\SE[45]There's nothing scary when we're together.
\SE[26]... I can't compete with you. Truly...

\SE[16]Don't show me that happy face...! \SE[48]That's why
I... I hate you...!!
